      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sensitivity analysis must demonstrate that choice of hemolysis damage model (power-law vs. strain-based) does not alter acceptance decision.",
      "rationale": "Only the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model was applied. No model-form uncertainty analysis comparing alternative hemolysis constitutive models was performed."
    },
    {
