      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sufficient experimental replicates must be available to characterize experimental variability for validation comparison.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark dataset provides three replicates per operating point; statistical power analysis indicates minimum five replicates required for MRL 5 validation at this uncertainty level."
