      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input parameters used in the validated model must be demonstrably equivalent to those applicable in the COU.",
      "rationale": "Hematocrit, plasma protein concentration, and temperature boundary conditions differ between validation experiments and COU operating envelope. Equivalency not established."
